Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.31,0:00:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72\\pos(960,1016)}Marvel's Phase 1 & 2 - A Look Back
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.99,0:00:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\\pos(960,1016)}I should't be alive,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.99,0:00:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\\pos(960,1016)}unless it was for a reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.50,0:00:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\\pos(960,1016)}I will protect Asgard and all the realms.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.05,0:00:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\\pos(960,1016)}You're nothing but a boy,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.47,0:00:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\\pos(960,1016)}trying to prove himself a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.14,0:00:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\\pos(960,1016)}You just don't know when to give up,do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.68,0:00:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\\pos(960,1016)}I can do this all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.77,0:00:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\\pos(960,1016)}I can not help you if you're gonna start all of this again.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.74,0:00:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\\pos(960,1016)}There is nothing except this.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.86,0:00:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\\pos(960,1016)}I just finally know what I have to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.20,0:01:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\\pos(960,1016)}These people are innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.12,0:01:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\\pos(960,1016)}Taking their lives will gain you nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.00,0:01:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\\pos(960,1016)}So take mine,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.50,0:01:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\\pos(960,1016)}and end this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.26,0:01:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\\pos(960,1016)}What made you so special?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.63,0:01:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\\pos(960,1016)}Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.22,0:01:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\\pos(960,1016)}I'm just a kid from Brooklyn.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.93,0:01:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\\pos(960,1016)}You think you're the only superhero in the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.90,0:01:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\\pos(960,1016)}You've become part of a bigger universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.56,0:01:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\\pos(960,1016)}You just don't know it yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.57,0:01:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\\pos(960,1016)}There was an idea,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.99,0:01:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\\pos(960,1016)}to bring together a group of remarkable people.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.41,0:01:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\\pos(960,1016)}See if they could work together,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.70,0:01:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\\pos(960,1016)}to fight the battles that we never could.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.33,0:01:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\\pos(960,1016)}There is no stopping it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.92,0:01:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\\pos(960,1016)}There is only the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.80,0:01:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\\pos(960,1016)}This is monsters and magic 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.76,0:02:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\\pos(960,1016)}and nothing we were ever trained for.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.89,0:02:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\\pos(960,1016)}You were made to be ruled.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.14,0:02:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\\pos(960,1016)}How desperate are you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.81,0:02:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\\pos(960,1016)}You call on such lost creatures to defend you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.48,0:02:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\\pos(960,1016)}There is no version of this where you come out on top.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.94,0:02:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\\pos(960,1016)}I have an army.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.03,0:02:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\\pos(960,1016)}We have a Hulk.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.62,0:02:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\\pos(960,1016)}Puny god.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.41,0:02:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\\pos(960,1016)}You start with something pure,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.29,0:02:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\\pos(960,1016)}something exciting.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.79,0:02:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\\pos(960,1016)}Then,come the mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.38,0:02:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\\pos(960,1016)}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.71,0:02:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\\pos(960,1016)}The compromises.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.14,0:02:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\\pos(960,1016)}The brutality,the sacrifice,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.68,0:02:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\\pos(960,1016)}it changes you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.52,0:02:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\\pos(960,1016)}I'd rather be a good man than a great king.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.61,0:02:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\\pos(960,1016)}The price of freedom is high.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.15,0:02:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\\pos(960,1016)}And it's a price I'm willing to pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.70,0:03:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\\pos(960,1016)}You can take away my house,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.49,0:03:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\\pos(960,1016)}all my tricks and toys.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.78,0:03:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\\pos(960,1016)}But I am Iron Man.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.50,0:03:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\\pos(960,1016)}Yes,the world is a vulnerable place.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.71,0:03:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\\pos(960,1016)}and yes,we help make it that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.72,0:03:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\\pos(960,1016)}But you need us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.43,0:03:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\\pos(960,1016)}You know why?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.44,0:03:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\\pos(960,1016)}Do enlighten us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.06,0:03:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\\pos(960,1016)}Because we're also the ones best qualified to defend it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.04,0:03:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\\pos(960,1016)}Humans,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.92,0:03:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\\pos(960,1016)}They are not the cowering wretches we were promised.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.13,0:04:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\\pos(960,1016)}To challenge them is to court death.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.72,0:04:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\\pos(960,1016)}I don't think you understand what you've started,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.77,0:04:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\\pos(960,1016)}letting the Avengers loose on the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.77,0:04:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\\pos(960,1016)}They're dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.10,0:04:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\\pos(960,1016)}They surely are.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.98,0:04:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\\pos(960,1016)}And the whole world knows it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.61,0:04:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\\pos(960,1016)}Every world knows it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.03,0:04:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\\pos(960,1016)}Bala bala bala...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.11,0:04:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\\pos(960,1016)}What the hell does that have to do with anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.53,0:04:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\\pos(960,1016)}The fate of 12 billion people,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.16,0:04:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\\pos(960,1016)}is in the hands of these criminals.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.75,0:04:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\\pos(960,1016)}I come from a planet of outlaws.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.54,0:04:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\\pos(960,1016)}******
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.42,0:04:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\\pos(960,1016)}Sounds like a place which I would like to visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.34,0:04:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\\pos(960,1016)}It's not a world of spies any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.97,0:04:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\\pos(960,1016)}Not even a world of heroes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.76,0:04:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\\pos(960,1016)}This is the age
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.02,0:04:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\\pos(960,1016)}of miracles.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.69,0:04:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\\pos(960,1016)}They've gone their separate ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.82,0:05:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\\pos(960,1016)}They'll come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.69,0:05:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\\pos(960,1016)}Because we'll need them to.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.53,0:05:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\\pos(960,1016)}Oh,Yeah.
